trans-unit.source: Represents the Visual Basic <see langword="Or" /> operator.

For <see langword="Boolean" /> operations, <see langword="False" /> if both <paramref name="Left" /> and <paramref name="Right" /> evaluate to <see langword="False" />; otherwise, <see langword="True" />.

trans-unit.source: For bitwise operations, 0 if both <paramref name="Left" /> and <paramref name="Right" /> evaluate to 0; otherwise, 1.
trans-unit.target: 비트 연산의 경우 <paramref name="Left" />와 <paramref name="Right" />이 모두 0으로 계산되면 0이고, 그렇지 않으면 1입니다.

trans-unit.source: The bit pattern to be shifted.

The data type must be an integral type (<see langword="SByte" />, <see langword="Byte" />, <see langword="Short" />, <see langword="UShort" />, <see langword="Integer" />, <see langword="UInteger" />, <see langword="Long" />, or <see langword="ULong" />).

trans-unit.source: The number of bits to shift the bit pattern.
The data type must be <see langword="Integer" /> or widen to <see langword="Integer" />.
trans-unit.target: 데이터 형식은 <see langword="Integer" />이거나 <see langword="Integer" />로 확장되어야 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Represents the Visual Basic <see langword="Xor" /> operator.
For a <see langword="Boolean" /> comparison, the return value is the logical exclusion (exclusive logical disjunction) of two <see langword="Boolean" /> values.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="Boolean" /> 비교의 경우 반환 값은 두 <see langword="Boolean" /> 값의 배타적 논리합입니다.

trans-unit.source: For bitwise (numeric) operations, the return value is a numeric value that represents the bitwise exclusion (exclusive bitwise disjunction) of two numeric bit patterns.
trans-unit.target: 비트(숫자) 연산의 경우 반환 값은 두 숫자 비트 패턴의 배타적 비트 논리합을 나타내는 숫자 값입니다.
